Invocation Name: roadstar
des:
Road Star provides customers stations addresses for Electric, Hybrid, Ethanol, Hydrogen, LPG,CNG and LNG fuel types, that are within the vicinity.
Road Star also provides policy information by state based on various categories like Tax, Grant, Rebate, Registration, Exemptions, Loans and Other Policies.
